.TH man 6 "09 Mar 2015" "1.0" "Happy Birthday man page"
.SH NAME
happy\-birthday \- wish you happy birthday, man!
.SH SYNOPSIS
happy\-birthday [YourName]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Today is your birthday! Happy birthday, man! It is important to be happy in such a day. All your frinds wish you a very nice day... and bash is your friend too! Let's enjoy together this moment.
.LP 
*****HAPPY BIRTHDAY*****
.LP
Wish you one hundred days like this and many more!
.BUGS
You should probably go out and drink something with your real-life friends instead of reading these lines.
